download the zip folder containing the GRID dataset using this link https://drive.google.com/file/d/19aAFZPlKxJPH5Q6ikqwMysrNgtnPvqwX/view?usp=drive_link
Follow the instructions in DLR/Instructions.txt
Run Modify_GRID to reorganize GRID in a structure compatible with the model
Run Modify_align_GRID.py onto the new modified GRID so that the labels stored in .align files are all in CAPITAL form
To run the test use the path of the newly modified GRID dataset on your local machine in --data_path
python main.py --gpu_id 0 --lip_model_path deep_lip_reading/lrs2_lip_model --data_path path_to_dataset/GRID_colored --data_list media/lrs2_test_samples.txt 
